opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 27th day of January, 2016, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus is DENIED. The Prothonota-ry is DIRECTED to strike the name of the jurists from the caption.
Justice EAKIN did not participate in the consideration or decision of this matter.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
